sentences.english: The police ferreted about all over the house for clues.
sentences.chinese: 线索把那屋子里里外外都搜遍了。

sentences.english: As I left home after breakfast, I shivered inwardly as well as outwardly.
sentences.chinese: 早餐之后我离开家的时候，我的里里外外都在颤抖。

sentences.english: I know every inch of Toad Hall, inside and out.
sentences.chinese: 蟾宫的里里外外，每一寸地方，我都了如指掌。

sentences.english: In in out out one handle, the poor family's child can get marry earlier.
sentences.chinese: 里里外外一把手，穷人的孩子早当家。

sentences.english: I know everything there is to know about the shrimping business.
sentences.chinese: 我知道虾的里里外外每件事。

sentences.english: Make sure the garage is well swilled out.
sentences.chinese: 请务必将车库里里外外都冲洗干净。

sentences.english: The man searched the whole house with a flashlight inside out.
sentences.chinese: 那人拿着电筒把整个屋子里里外外搜查了一遍。

sentences.english: More trees will be planed in and aroud our village.
sentences.chinese: 我们乡村的里里外外要莳植更多的树。

sentences.english: The box was painted within and without.
sentences.chinese: 盒子里里外外都漆过了。
